<plot>An older woman (Ruth Cracknell) does not speak to her daughter and detests everything about her. The only solace is with her regular visits to the doctor who drops her off along the road to spend her day in the countryside alone. One day at her favourite place in the country the older lady meets a young girl (Elizabeth Crosby) who is having relationship problems with her boyfriend, and they share their bitter memories. These meetings become regular therapeutic sessions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?591060</url></doc>
